{
  "stem": "26983.11",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 25.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember one was even a Czech kind of kapo.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was a good man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But his nerves were in such a stage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I've never seen somebody so nervous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "A bundle of nerves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But he didn't beat us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he behaved.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They put us in the beginning in barracks, and slowly they divided us into little groups.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they older ones had to do all kinds of works.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I remember the conditions were horrible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we slept somehow on the floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Slept is understatement.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like sardines.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean my head on foot of somebody else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So always head and foot, head and foot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were squeezing us really like sardines.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The trouble was if somebody wanted to get out at night, he couldn't more squeeze himself into the last position.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then there was a shortage of water and of food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had less and less food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I do remember, we came to again a closed block.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The blockeldester was [INAUDIBLE] against [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[GERMAN] was a kind of the second after the blockeldester.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Both were German criminals.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Sadists like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I didn't--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sadists.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--so before.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They behaved in the most outrageous cruel way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They [INAUDIBLE] us and--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Always they wanted to clean the block, so it doesn't matter if it was snow or terrible weather, we had to go out and some of them had to clean the floor in this block.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We meanwhile could die of cold and this terrible winter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The children and grown ups, partisans from Yugoslavia, I remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was behaving in most cruel way.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
